720
00:28:18,198 --> 00:28:20,190
Yes, it is.

721
00:28:20,231 --> 00:28:22,190
And if they did it to us,
they did it to others.

722
00:28:22,231 --> 00:28:24,613
I'm gonna tell them I'm going to
the DOJ if they don't back off.

723
00:28:24,653 --> 00:28:27,010
No, without proof, a threat
like that could be construed

724
00:28:27,051 --> 00:28:29,071
as inducing
malicious prosecution.

725
00:28:29,112 --> 00:28:29,694
You can't do it.

726
00:28:29,735 --> 00:28:31,112
Well, I have to do something.

727
00:28:31,153 --> 00:28:33,174
Because instead of spending
my time last night

728
00:28:33,215 --> 00:28:34,392
thinking about
how to prevent this,

729
00:28:34,432 --> 00:28:35,807
I took my eye off the ball.

730
00:28:35,848 --> 00:28:37,899
Katrina, don't be so hard
on yourself.

731
00:28:38,464 --> 00:28:40,343
You couldn't
have seen this coming.

732
00:28:40,384 --> 00:28:41,801
